                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-49737676" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="49737676">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2715929/">低垂的柳絮</a>
                    <span>2008-07-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">昨日之我与今日之我本身便有种超越的意味在里面，梁任公有云：“以今日之我攻昨日之我。”反思与超越让当代历史研究的路向越发的广泛。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="940194590">
        <div class="comment">
